{"tid":707030,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"撲走美斯12碼　 冰島門神賽後獲Eason頒獎","createTime":"2018-06-18T10:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T11:30:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"693d9e4774073c12912d82b0115bf5ece7a057fd","tid":707030,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T10:57:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180618/20423703\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180618%2F20423703&d=nvueCfnSCfy7NfZdOypNw9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=391fe7bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180618%2F20423703&h=967fdb2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180618/20423703</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月18日 <br />\n<br />\n撲走美斯12碼　<br />\n冰島門神賽後獲Eason頒獎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180618/large/a0403a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180618%2Flarge%2Fa0403a.gif&h=4f51559c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n【本報訊】世盃D組首輪賽事，神奇球隊冰島憑門將荷杜臣撲走美斯主射的12碼，以1:1逼和出線大熱阿根廷，賽後荷杜臣更當選為今場比賽的最佳球員，在香港歌手陳奕迅（Eason）手中接過獎項（圖）。原來這位冰島門神不但撲救了得，更曾當導演拍攝電影及MV。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全職踢波前兼任導演<br />\n<br />\n獲贊助商邀請觀賞世盃的Eason，在fb個人專頁留言兼上載頒獎合照：「原本當導演的他，擋掉了漂亮的一球，也成為了今晚的Man of the Match！恭喜你，Mr. Hannes T萡r Halld萡rsson！」Eason與經理人甘菁菁都現場觀看冰島對阿根廷一戰，更大讚氣氛很好，甘菁菁說：「他（Eason）覺得很榮幸，首次見到球員從球員通道走回來，並在後台頒獎。」她補充Eason是世盃贊助商的代言人，每場賽後都會由這品牌的各地代言人頒發該場最佳球員獎。<br />\n<br />\n現年34歲的荷杜臣，2012年曾為冰島歌手Greta Salome&amp; Jonsi拍攝歌曲《Never Forget》的MV，還接了不少商業廣告當導演。<br />\n<br />\n然而他未有放棄成為守門員的夢想，自2002年起一度在國內低組別球會效力，直至2011年才首獲國家隊垂青，荷杜臣在2016年歐國盃後曾言：「過去有九年我主要職業是電影導演，我無法像其他職業足球員一樣，之前大部份收入都是源自導演工作。」他2015年獲荷甲奈梅亨垂青，放下導演工作；然而今年34歲的他有傳會在世盃後掛靴，然後回歸電影圈。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n酒店check-in等成粒鐘<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n地上最強：德國盛衰與拜仁同步&ndash;&ndash;蔡子強<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n酒店check-in等成粒鐘<br />\n<br />\n地上最強：德國盛衰與拜仁同步&ndash;&ndash;蔡子強<br />\n<br />\n老少女睇波日記<br />\n<br />\n的士撞人　恐襲驚魂　球迷：未驚過"},{"pid":"e35264d92c0230c08d7dcb81d68cf9aa6cc4f2f9","tid":707030,"uid":132587,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T11:00:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/0466286ca36748dce582d06bf77e86ca/tenor.gif?itemid=4519872\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2F0466286ca36748dce582d06bf77e86ca%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D4519872&h=c69f7bf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個冰島門將心諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78547ddc4bc9e3ef159918fbb0ce9d112b05288","tid":707030,"uid":48222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T11:03:29.000Z","msg":"咩料呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f2ece8607366182b2936ca8104291af97d18e33","tid":707030,"uid":59952,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T11:04:56.000Z","msg":"eason可能心諗想頒俾美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9389b30ff42fadf3e02a5dfd00f1526088db8243","tid":707030,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T11:07:41.000Z","msg":"送禮臣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced858f7d0478d4290d2a53f1837c53593f46fad","tid":707030,"uid":9694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T11:11:26.000Z","msg":"Mr. Hannes T萡r Halld萡rsson！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d873db3f62cb2b9851805f9d6f34708776a911a","tid":707030,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9389b30